WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.830
Hey, good morning, family. How are y'all

00:00:02.840 --> 00:00:05.910
doing today? Glory to God. Well, it

00:00:05.910 --> 00:00:05.920
looked

00:00:05.920 --> 00:00:08.150
like we had some victory when it comes to

00:00:08.160 --> 00:00:09.830
the hurricane. It went from a

00:00:09.840 --> 00:00:12.710
Category 5 to

00:00:12.720 --> 00:00:15.110
a Category 3, and I believe that's by

00:00:15.120 --> 00:00:17.550
the prayers of the righteous, praying and

00:00:17.560 --> 00:00:19.870
believing for that thing to fall

00:00:19.880 --> 00:00:21.670
apart. You know what? It could have

00:00:21.680 --> 00:00:24.550
been a lot worse. It

00:00:24.560 --> 00:00:26.070
could have been a lot worse if it would

00:00:26.080 --> 00:00:28.510
have hit at what it was when it was in

00:00:28.520 --> 00:00:31.670
the Gulf, but God, who is rich

00:00:31.680 --> 00:00:35.390
in mercy. I just want to say,

00:00:35.400 --> 00:00:36.750
we're doing it, folks. This is

00:00:36.750 --> 00:00:36.760
why

00:00:36.760 --> 00:00:38.710
we're here. That's why the Lord said,

00:00:38.720 --> 00:00:40.710
'Hey, Brandon, I want you to go on and

00:00:40.720 --> 00:00:42.510
do these prayer videos for the next

00:00:42.520 --> 00:00:44.830
30 days.'Now, we're going to take

00:00:44.840 --> 00:00:47.630
communion today again, so if you

00:00:47.630 --> 00:00:47.640
are

00:00:47.640 --> 00:00:50.190
new here and you didn't pray with

00:00:50.200 --> 00:00:51.710
us yesterday or the day before,

00:00:51.720 --> 00:00:53.550
today's your day, and I'm excited

00:00:53.560 --> 00:00:56.310
you're here. But we have a mission,

00:00:56.320 --> 00:00:59.150
and it is to disrupt the things of the

00:00:59.160 --> 00:01:03.030
devil. He is not going to have victory

00:01:03.040 --> 00:01:05.710
in this earth as long as we're here; we

00:01:05.720 --> 00:01:08.070
have authority over him, and we're going

00:01:08.080 --> 00:01:10.630
to rise up and take our authority over

00:01:10.640 --> 00:01:12.710
the devil. We don't need to go around

00:01:12.720 --> 00:01:14.390
hitting the devil in the head like those

00:01:14.390 --> 00:01:14.400
Whac-A-Mole—you

00:01:14.400 --> 00:01:15.350
know, those

00:01:15.360 --> 00:01:17.350
Whac-A-Moles at the fair that

00:01:17.350 --> 00:01:17.360
are

00:01:17.360 --> 00:01:18.510
always sticking up.

00:01:18.510 --> 00:01:18.520
I've

00:01:18.520 --> 00:01:19.990
told everybody this: it's like we're

00:01:20.000 --> 00:01:22.230
always trying to wait and put out the

00:01:22.240 --> 00:01:25.030
devil's fires. The

00:01:25.040 --> 00:01:26.390
body of Christ is running around with

00:01:26.390 --> 00:01:26.400
a

00:01:26.400 --> 00:01:27.910
fire hose, always putting out the

00:01:27.920 --> 00:01:29.910
devil's fires. I said it

00:01:29.910 --> 00:01:29.920
is

00:01:29.920 --> 00:01:33.550
ridiculous. We are watchmen. We see

00:01:33.560 --> 00:01:36.190
far in advance—sometimes I see years,

00:01:36.200 --> 00:01:38.390
sometimes I see days, sometimes I see

00:01:38.400 --> 00:01:40.870
even more than five years.

00:01:40.880 --> 00:01:43.430
We'll

00:01:43.440 --> 00:01:45.990
be up on the wall and we'll see things

00:01:46.000 --> 00:01:48.230
coming, but we know we're going to put

00:01:48.240 --> 00:01:50.990
out the fire before he starts it.

00:01:51.000 --> 00:01:53.470
That's why the Holy Spirit warns us

00:01:53.480 --> 00:01:56.150
and guides us about all things.

00:01:56.160 --> 00:01:57.670
He doesn't want us to be caught off

00:01:57.680 --> 00:02:00.030
guard.

00:02:00.040 --> 00:02:01.830
Was the hurricane

00:02:01.840 --> 00:02:04.030
catching us off guard? No. We know that there

00:02:04.030 --> 00:02:04.040
are

00:02:04.040 --> 00:02:05.790
going to be things, but we have

00:02:05.800 --> 00:02:07.670
authority over them.

00:02:07.680 --> 00:02:09.749
We know that we're in the end times. We

00:02:09.759 --> 00:02:11.590
know, ladies and gentlemen, that

00:02:11.600 --> 00:02:13.790
as labor pains come upon a woman,

00:02:13.800 --> 00:02:15.990
so will it be. We know it's going to get

00:02:16.000 --> 00:02:18.390
darker and darker because the Bible told

00:02:18.400 --> 00:02:21.630
us it would. Can we stop it all? No, we

00:02:21.640 --> 00:02:23.590
can't, because some things are going to

00:02:23.600 --> 00:02:26.710
happen, but we can protect our families.

00:02:26.720 --> 00:02:28.230
You don't have to walk in fear of the

00:02:28.240 --> 00:02:30.110
devil. You don't have to walk in

00:02:30.120 --> 00:02:32.470
bondage. For

00:02:32.480 --> 00:02:34.230
me and my house,

00:02:34.240 --> 00:02:36.390
I always say, 'Let the

00:02:36.400 --> 00:02:38.790
storm rage outside, but there's peace on

00:02:38.800 --> 00:02:40.270
the

00:02:40.270 --> 00:02:40.280
inside.'I

00:02:40.280 --> 00:02:43.430
am not going to have the devil stir up

00:02:43.440 --> 00:02:45.710
a storm inside and outside. You

00:02:45.720 --> 00:02:47.470
do what you've got to do; I'm going

00:02:47.480 --> 00:02:48.550
to take authority over here, and I put a

00:02:48.560 --> 00:02:50.510
bloodline around my house. I take

00:02:50.520 --> 00:02:54.030
communion daily. I take my

00:02:54.040 --> 00:02:56.030
seat and I sit with Him.

00:02:56.040 --> 00:02:57.390
Everybody says, 'Well, you pray too

00:02:57.400 --> 00:02:59.830
long. Your videos go too

00:02:59.830 --> 00:02:59.840
long.'If

00:02:59.840 --> 00:03:02.030
you're only praying

00:03:02.030 --> 00:03:02.040
ten

00:03:02.040 --> 00:03:03.990
minutes a day, you're in trouble because

00:03:03.990 --> 00:03:04.000
of

00:03:04.000 --> 00:03:05.790
what I've seen coming.

00:03:05.800 --> 00:03:07.110
People don't want to hear that in the

00:03:07.120 --> 00:03:08.590
Word of Faith circles because they think

00:03:08.600 --> 00:03:10.230
you're being negative, but I'm

00:03:10.240 --> 00:03:11.870
trying to tell you and warn you as a

00:03:11.880 --> 00:03:14.830
watchman that there's a storm coming.

00:03:14.840 --> 00:03:16.350
I'm trying to tell you that we have

00:03:16.360 --> 00:03:18.030
authority over the storm. There

00:03:18.030 --> 00:03:18.040
are

00:03:18.040 --> 00:03:20.150
economic things coming

00:03:20.150 --> 00:03:20.160
and

00:03:20.160 --> 00:03:22.670
hard days for some

00:03:22.680 --> 00:03:25.070
people, but we don't have to

00:03:25.080 --> 00:03:27.070
participate in it.

00:03:27.080 --> 00:03:29.590
It's not for us; we're His beloved. He

00:03:29.600 --> 00:03:32.030
will always take care of

00:03:32.030 --> 00:03:32.040
His

00:03:32.040 --> 00:03:34.310
beloved. He's not up there warning

00:03:34.310 --> 00:03:34.320
me,

00:03:34.320 --> 00:03:35.710
'Oh, Brandon, guess what? Doom

00:03:35.720 --> 00:03:37.430
and gloom is coming for you.'No, I'm in a

00:03:37.440 --> 00:03:39.510
covenant with Him. This is part of my

00:03:39.520 --> 00:03:42.430
covenant: His body, His blood. I take it

00:03:42.440 --> 00:03:45.710
inside of me and I say, 'No, thus far

00:03:45.720 --> 00:03:47.470
and no further, devil.'There are no

00:03:47.480 --> 00:03:50.470
plagues, no pestilence. Psalm 91.

00:03:50.480 --> 00:03:53.270
Just remember what I told you all:

00:03:53.280 --> 00:03:56.150
I said there was a great storm coming on

00:03:56.160 --> 00:03:57.510
the East Coast. Everybody said, 'Well,

00:03:57.510 --> 00:03:57.520
was

00:03:57.520 --> 00:03:59.470
that Milton? Was that

00:03:59.480 --> 00:04:01.550
the hurricanes

00:04:01.550 --> 00:04:01.560
coming?'No.

00:04:01.560 --> 00:04:04.190
This was about the Antichrist

00:04:04.200 --> 00:04:07.950
system, the Antichrist agenda that was trying

00:04:07.960 --> 00:04:09.990
to come on. I could

00:04:10.000 --> 00:04:12.510
see the bands of the hurricane on the

00:04:12.520 --> 00:04:14.390
East Coast that was coming from the

00:04:14.400 --> 00:04:16.750
Gulf. What I saw was not coming from the

00:04:16.760 --> 00:04:18.390
Gulf; it was coming from the East Coast.

00:04:18.400 --> 00:04:20.990
It was a massive storm that went all the

00:04:20.990 --> 00:04:21.000
way

00:04:21.000 --> 00:04:23.790
from sea to shining

00:04:23.790 --> 00:04:23.800
sea,

00:04:23.800 --> 00:04:25.630
from the south all the way to the

00:04:25.640 --> 00:04:28.630
north. It was from coast to coast.

00:04:30.520 --> 00:04:33.670
This was a massive storm

00:04:33.680 --> 00:04:35.190
and the bands started

00:04:35.200 --> 00:04:37.150
coming upon the land.

00:04:37.160 --> 00:04:39.870
The Lord said to me, 'Remember,

00:04:39.880 --> 00:04:43.990
I saw a massive Holy Ghost

00:04:43.990 --> 00:04:44.000
wall.'I

00:04:44.000 --> 00:04:45.190
have to be careful with that word

00:04:45.190 --> 00:04:45.200
because

00:04:45.200 --> 00:04:47.790
last time people got mad at

00:04:47.790 --> 00:04:47.800
me—a

00:04:47.800 --> 00:04:50.630
massive Holy Ghost barrier.

00:04:52.840 --> 00:04:54.590
These people are so liberal and

00:04:54.600 --> 00:04:55.630
dumb...

00:04:55.630 --> 00:04:55.640
there

00:04:55.640 --> 00:04:57.430
was

00:04:57.440 --> 00:05:00.790
a wall of

00:05:06.720 --> 00:05:09.430
protection for the body

00:05:09.440 --> 00:05:12.110
of Christ.

00:05:12.120 --> 00:05:15.150
I asked the Lord, and it was thick

00:05:15.150 --> 00:05:15.160
with

00:05:15.160 --> 00:05:18.190
humongous bricks.

00:05:18.200 --> 00:05:20.550
It was like four feet thick

00:05:21.840 --> 00:05:23.790
in each sector.

00:05:23.800 --> 00:05:27.870
On

00:05:27.880 --> 00:05:31.750
this side was a green valley with

00:05:31.750 --> 00:05:31.760
a

00:05:31.760 --> 00:05:34.190
little house that had a chimney.

00:05:34.200 --> 00:05:36.190
Smoke was coming up

00:05:36.200 --> 00:05:38.030
through the chimney, and there was

00:05:38.030 --> 00:05:38.040
fresh-baked

00:05:38.040 --> 00:05:41.590
bread inside of this little

00:05:41.600 --> 00:05:44.150
fire stove. They were cooking this

00:05:44.160 --> 00:05:46.110
bread, and in the

00:05:46.120 --> 00:05:48.430
spirit, I could smell the bread that God

00:05:48.440 --> 00:05:50.990
had prepared for me. You could see

00:05:51.000 --> 00:05:53.110
the stream of water that was

00:05:53.120 --> 00:05:55.230
still and in peace. The brook was so

00:05:55.240 --> 00:05:57.150
clear, it looked like you could just

00:06:00.040 --> 00:06:01.470
lap it up because it

00:06:01.480 --> 00:06:03.390
looked like the best water ever.

00:06:03.400 --> 00:06:05.670
Thank God for that. There was

00:06:05.680 --> 00:06:08.270
a table set up perfectly

00:06:08.270 --> 00:06:08.280
with

00:06:08.280 --> 00:06:10.150
all these dishes.

00:06:10.160 --> 00:06:12.510
The Lord

00:06:12.520 --> 00:06:14.430
said to me,

00:06:37.600 --> 00:06:39.910
'Brandon, this is

00:06:39.910 --> 00:06:39.920
Psalm

00:06:39.920 --> 00:06:45.710
91 and Psalm 23

00:06:45.710 --> 00:06:45.720
combined.'I

00:06:45.720 --> 00:06:48.670
have prepared a table before

00:06:48.680 --> 00:06:51.230
you in the presence of your enemies.

00:06:55.480 --> 00:06:57.590
He's the Shepherd; we shall not want. He

00:06:57.590 --> 00:06:57.600
makes

00:06:57.600 --> 00:07:00.310
us lie down in green pastures; He

00:07:00.320 --> 00:07:02.790
leads us beside the still waters.

00:07:02.800 --> 00:07:04.750
That water was

00:07:04.760 --> 00:07:07.390
beautiful and perfect.

00:07:09.880 --> 00:07:12.070
You could smell the

00:07:12.070 --> 00:07:12.080
fresh-baked

00:07:12.080 --> 00:07:15.510
bread; it was just perfect. But there

00:07:15.520 --> 00:07:17.630
was a wall there.

00:07:17.640 --> 00:07:19.390
The name of the Lord is a

00:07:19.400 --> 00:07:21.350
strong tower, and the righteous run into

00:07:21.360 --> 00:07:22.910
it and they are safe.

00:07:25.160 --> 00:07:27.190
He's our shield and

00:07:27.200 --> 00:07:29.230
our buckler. There was

00:07:33.440 --> 00:07:36.230
a place of protection there.

00:07:38.040 --> 00:07:41.070
On the other side was a massive storm.

00:07:41.080 --> 00:07:43.710
He says, 'As long as you get

00:07:43.710 --> 00:07:43.720
Psalm

00:07:43.720 --> 00:07:47.150
91 and Psalm 23 deep down in your

00:07:47.160 --> 00:07:50.230
heart, that storm that's coming

00:07:50.240 --> 00:07:53.190
won't get on the inside of you.'You have

00:07:53.200 --> 00:07:58.150
got to get Psalm 23 and Psalm 91 deep

00:07:58.160 --> 00:08:00.710
down inside of your heart,

00:08:00.720 --> 00:08:04.910
not just by memorization, but

00:08:04.920 --> 00:08:05.950
so

00:08:05.960 --> 00:08:08.430
that you can quote it backwards

00:08:08.430 --> 00:08:08.440
and

00:08:08.440 --> 00:08:11.430
sideways.

00:08:15.120 --> 00:08:18.430
Meditate on it, renew your mind to

00:08:18.430 --> 00:08:18.440
Psalm

00:08:18.440 --> 00:08:22.470
23 and Psalm 91.

00:08:22.480 --> 00:08:24.590
Get it in you;

00:08:24.600 --> 00:08:27.230
mutter it like a cow eats cud. You know how

00:08:27.230 --> 00:08:27.240
they

00:08:27.240 --> 00:08:29.710
spit up the old grass

00:08:29.720 --> 00:08:31.310
and chew on it again? They have all those

00:08:31.320 --> 00:08:35.029
stomachs to chew on that grass.

00:08:35.029 --> 00:08:35.039
Well,

00:08:35.039 --> 00:08:36.990
spew the Word of God up out of you

00:08:37.000 --> 00:08:38.550
and chew it

00:08:38.560 --> 00:08:40.149
like cud.

00:08:40.159 --> 00:08:41.950
It's an old country term, but

00:08:41.960 --> 00:08:43.469
it's the truth.

00:08:43.479 --> 00:08:45.070
Get that Word down inside

00:08:46.830 --> 00:08:46.840
you.

00:08:49.360 --> 00:08:50.390
The Lord said, 'Brandon, you need to

00:08:50.400 --> 00:08:52.430
increase your scripture

00:08:52.430 --> 00:08:52.440
reading.'He

00:08:52.440 --> 00:08:53.630
told me that when I'd been going to

00:08:53.640 --> 00:08:55.550
these meetings with Nancy

00:08:55.550 --> 00:08:55.560
Dufresne

00:08:55.560 --> 00:08:59.590
and this healing thing.

00:08:59.600 --> 00:09:01.830
What she was talking

00:09:01.830 --> 00:09:01.840
about—getting

00:09:01.840 --> 00:09:03.150
that Word down inside

00:09:03.150 --> 00:09:03.160
you—went

00:09:03.160 --> 00:09:04.790
along with

00:09:04.800 --> 00:09:06.230
what the Holy Spirit told me. It was

00:09:06.240 --> 00:09:07.710
confirmation.

00:09:10.680 --> 00:09:13.470
He said it's time

00:09:13.480 --> 00:09:16.270
for you to get that Word even deeper

00:09:16.280 --> 00:09:19.230
down inside of your spirit.

00:09:20.840 --> 00:09:23.070
Faith comes by hearing, and hearing by

00:09:23.080 --> 00:09:25.270
the Word of God.

00:09:25.280 --> 00:09:27.670
So when the storms come,

00:09:27.680 --> 00:09:30.750
your house is built on the rock.

00:09:30.760 --> 00:09:33.110
Your house is not built on the sands of

00:09:33.120 --> 00:09:34.990
life

00:09:34.990 --> 00:09:35.000
so

00:09:35.000 --> 00:09:36.990
the storm knocks

00:09:36.990 --> 00:09:37.000
it

00:09:37.000 --> 00:09:39.470
down. You've got to have your house on

00:09:39.470 --> 00:09:39.480
a

00:09:39.480 --> 00:09:41.590
firm foundation.

00:09:52.960 --> 00:09:54.590
Faith works by love, too.

00:09:54.600 --> 00:09:56.270
You've got to get your love

00:09:56.280 --> 00:09:58.270
walk right. You've got to treat people

00:09:58.280 --> 00:10:00.750
good and walk in love.

00:10:00.760 --> 00:10:03.790
If you say,

00:10:03.800 --> 00:10:05.830
'Why is my faith not

00:10:05.830 --> 00:10:05.840
working?'check

00:10:05.840 --> 00:10:08.390
your love thermostat. If

00:10:08.400 --> 00:10:10.310
you're not

00:10:10.320 --> 00:10:12.390
treating people right—I'm always quick

00:10:12.400 --> 00:10:15.150
to repent if I snap at my wife or my

00:10:15.160 --> 00:10:17.990
kids.

00:10:17.990 --> 00:10:18.000
I

00:10:18.000 --> 00:10:20.590
instantaneously

00:10:20.600 --> 00:10:22.230
say, 'Holy Spirit,

00:10:22.240 --> 00:10:25.110
always be quick to correct

00:10:25.110 --> 00:10:25.120
me.'It's

00:10:25.120 --> 00:10:26.950
never

00:10:26.960 --> 00:10:29.670
right to be cranky. You've got to walk in

00:10:29.680 --> 00:10:31.990
love.

00:10:33.720 --> 00:10:36.630
I have learned a lot over the last

00:10:36.640 --> 00:10:39.550
year walking this channel out

00:10:39.560 --> 00:10:42.390
by faith. The Lord is doing so

00:10:42.400 --> 00:10:44.190
much, and He keeps telling me,

00:10:44.200 --> 00:10:45.670
'Brandon, you've got to spend more time

00:10:45.680 --> 00:10:47.550
with Me. You've got to separate yourself unto

00:10:47.550 --> 00:10:47.560
Me.'I

00:10:47.560 --> 00:10:49.070
get

00:10:49.080 --> 00:10:50.990
distracted with doing eBay and Poshmark,

00:10:51.000 --> 00:10:53.310
and

00:10:53.320 --> 00:10:54.470
He says, 'Brandon, you've got to

00:10:54.480 --> 00:10:56.990
take some time and pray

00:10:58.950 --> 00:10:58.960
more.'I'm

00:11:00.720 --> 00:11:03.829
learning.

00:11:05.600 --> 00:11:08.590
Glory to God. I just want

00:11:08.600 --> 00:11:11.270
to say thank you all for being here.

00:11:13.240 --> 00:11:15.750
We're going to take

00:11:15.760 --> 00:11:18.030
communion and we're going to pray.

00:11:18.040 --> 00:11:19.990
I feel the leading of the Holy

00:11:20.000 --> 00:11:22.710
Spirit to pray today about the people

00:11:22.710 --> 00:11:22.720
being protected

00:11:22.720 --> 00:11:24.870
after Milton,

00:11:27.880 --> 00:11:31.110
but we've also got to pray over the

00:11:31.120 --> 00:11:32.390
election.

00:11:32.400 --> 00:11:34.270
The Lord said for the next 30

00:11:34.280 --> 00:11:36.150
days to pray over the

00:11:36.160 --> 00:11:38.470
election. I

00:11:38.480 --> 00:11:43.510
saw a week's span of time

00:11:46.080 --> 00:11:47.590
bolded:

00:11:49.880 --> 00:11:53.190
Wednesday, Thursday, Friday.

00:11:53.200 --> 00:11:54.870
I

00:11:54.880 --> 00:11:56.870
saw

00:11:56.880 --> 00:11:59.310
a secret plan

00:11:59.310 --> 00:11:59.320
where

00:11:59.320 --> 00:12:01.430
all hidden things will be revealed.

